metadata.name: Dandies Original Logo 2019
metadata.description: Dandies Beard Barbershop is a community-owned barbershop that believes in fair wages for all.  The first barbershop in history to be started by Sikh Beard Barber, Money Singh.   Dandies believes in ethical barbering art and takes home net 5%, rest of the money is distributed within barbers and the community.   By buying this NFT, you are supporting "Dandies" in REAL LIFE. Dandies NFT owners will also get an opportunity to visit place in real life in Mountain View California and be able to attend VIP events for exclusively for NFT owners  If or when we go public, we will be giving share in stocks to Dandies NFT members first before going public
